reviewText: fun pack for good musicals and great performances by Hutton, Day and Reynolds.

When I ordered this set on August 20, I planned on reviewing these musicals in just a few weeks. Four months later, they haven't been shipped. The latest estimate for a shipping date indicates that I'll get them next year.

I would love to give you a review of these three movies that I ordered on July 7, 2006, but as of November 4th (today) I have not yet received them.  I am really looking forward to getting these old movies - much better than most of the new movies now being made.
